      • getDWd

        public Double getDWd()
        How much to nudge wind direction to perform probabilistic analysis on weather. Applied after all patches and grids, and does not recalculate any FWI calculations. Applied before any FBP calculations. Provided in compass degrees, -360 to 360 is acceptable. Applied to both simulations, and to instantaneous calculations as shown on the map trace view query, for consistency. Primarily used when weather information does not have the expected fidelity.

      • setDWd

        public void setDWd(Double dWd)
        How much to nudge wind direction to perform probabilistic analysis on weather. Applied after all patches and grids, and does not recalculate any FWI calculations. Applied before any FBP calculations. Provided in compass degrees, -360 to 360 is acceptable. Applied to both simulations, and to instantaneous calculations as shown on the map trace view query, for consistency. Primarily used when weather information does not have the expected fidelity.
